# Commit Message Template

# Format: <type>(<scope>): [Task X.X] - <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# <footer>
#
# Types:
#   feat:     New feature
#   fix:      Bug fix
#   docs:     Documentation only
#   style:    Code style changes (formatting, etc.)
#   refactor: Code refactoring
#   test:     Adding or updating tests
#   chore:    Maintenance tasks
#   build:    Build system changes
#   ci:       CI/CD changes
#
# Scope: poc-0, poc-1, poc-2, poc-3, or specific component
#
# Examples:
#   feat(poc-0): [Task 1.1] - Initialize Nx workspace
#   fix(poc-0): [Task 2.2] - Fix Vite configuration for shell
#   test(poc-0): [Task 6.1] - Add tests for HelloRemote component
#
# Body (optional):
#   - What was done
#   - Why it was done
#   - Any breaking changes
#
# Footer (optional):
#   - Closes #issue
#   - References task number
#
# Example:
#   feat(poc-0): [Task 1.1] - Initialize Nx workspace
#
#   - Created Nx workspace with React preset
#   - Configured pnpm as package manager
#   - Set up basic workspace structure
#
#   References: docs/POC-0-Implementation/implementation-plan.md#task-11
